      1          /**
      2           *  @file
      3           *  @defgroup   CLASS_B
      4           *  @brief      This module implements the standard API (Application Programming Interface) for
      5           *              STM32G0x Micro module.
      6           *
      7           *  @details    This module provides the interface to the application to configure the controller and to perform the
      8           *              CLASSB safety relevant controller tests.
      9           *
     10           *              Configuring the Controller such as-
     11           *              Initializing microcontroller bus clock, configuring clock for microcontroller,
     12           *              Configures the controller to work either in slow, normal or sleep mode of operation,
     13           *              servicing Window and Independent watchdog,
     14           *              enabling/disabling or store/restoring of the interrupts,
     15           *              Providing FLASH size ,RAM size and ID of microcontroller,
     16           *              provision to detect Low voltage.
     17           *
     18           *              CLASS B safety-relevant controller test during boot as well as run time such as -
     19           *              CPU Register Test,
     20           *              Watchdog test,
     21           *              RAM Test(at boot time),
     22           *              Flash test
     23           *              stack test
     24           *
     25           * @section    Applicable_Documents
     26           *                  List here all the applicable documents if needed. <tr>
     27           *
     28           * $Header: $
     29           *
     30           *  @copyright  Copyright 2017. Whirlpool Corporation. All rights reserved - CONFIDENTIAL
     31            */
