    472           *    @return   MICRO_LVD_STATUS_TYPE :
    473           *               MICRO_LVD_DISABLED              - If the LVD is disabled
    474           *               MICRO_LVD_ENABLED_NOT_DETECTING - The LVD is enabled and low voltage threshold condition not happened
